# Provider API keys (see spec §7.2). The default model-catalog.json only uses
# the `ollama` provider, which needs no key, so this file is optional for the
# default configuration. Copy to `.env` and fill in if you switch the catalog
# to a hosted provider.

# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# CLAUDE_API_KEY=...
# GEMINI_API_KEY=...
# DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=...
